nodes.text: Liriana: Dark Force Witch of Cularin

Liriana: Dark Force Witch of Cularin is an article written by Morrie Mullins. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on September 13 2001. It beings with an in-universe transmission from Dariana of the Hiironi irstat requesting a group of heroes to help against the Wyrd and explaining their current leader. This is followed by out-of-universe bios and stats.
